text: "I Go to Sleep" is a 1965 song by The Kinks and has been covered by numerous artists including The Pretenders in 1981 where it went to number 6 in Belgium, number 7 in the United Kingdom, number 9 in the Netherlands and number 28 in New Zealand. ==References== Category:1965 songs Category:The Kinks songs Category:The Pretenders songs Category:Peggy Lee songs Category:Sia songs Category:Cher songs Category:Baroque pop songs
title: I Go to Sleep
